OL,3,CFashion show celebrates disability,
OL,4,Cinclusion and adaptive fashion
OL,6,FModels from across the North West are
OL,7,Fset to take to the catwalk tonight as
OL,8,FManchester hosts its first Disability
OL,9,FPride Catwalk.
OL,11,FThe catwalk, held at Aviva Studios,
OL,12,Fcelebrates disability, body confidence
OL,13,Fand inclusive fashion.
OL,15,FThe event will see 16 disabled,
OL,16,Fneurodivergent and chronically ill
OL,17,Fmodels showcase adaptive clothing
OL,18,Fdesigned to challenge traditional
OL,19,Fideas of fashion, while highlighting
OL,20,Fthe importance of accessibility and
OL,21,Frepresentation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
