FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782733687
OL,3,CFashion show celebrates disability,
OL,4,Cinclusion and adaptive fashion
OL,6,FThe show has been organised by
OL,7,FManchester Metropolitan University
OL,8,Ffashion graduate Ellie Brown, who
OL,9,Ffounded the label after experiencing
OL,10,Ffirst-hand how inaccessible clothing
OL,11,Fcan be following a serious ankle
OL,12,Finjury.
OL,14,F"The standards that the fashion
OL,15,Findustry runs by at the moment are
OL,16,Foutdated and we need to throw them in
OL,17,Fthe bin, and start working towards
OL,18,Fincluding everyone in fashion", Ellie
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
