OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782733687
OL,3,CFashion show celebrates disability,
OL,4,Cinclusion and adaptive fashion
OL,6,FA purpose-built runway has also been
OL,7,Fcreated for the event, including a
OL,8,Fdouble-height bar designed to be
OL,9,Faccessible for wheelchair users.
OL,11,FAmong those taking part is content
OL,12,Fcreator Lucy Jane, who has openly
OL,13,Fdocumented her experience of living
OL,14,Fwith Ulcerative Colitis and a stoma
OL,15,Facross social media.
OL,17,FShe hopes walking the runway will help
OL,18,Fchallenge misconceptions while
OL,19,Fencouraging others to
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
