OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782733687
OL,3,CFashion show celebrates disability,
OL,4,Cinclusion and adaptive fashion
OL,6,Fembrace their bodies with confidence:
OL,7,F"Inclusive fashion is so important
OL,8,Fbecause seeing yourself represented in
OL,9,Fthe media can make such a big impact.
OL,11,F"It's so easy to represent these
OL,12,Fpeople because there are so many of us
OL,13,Fliving with disabilities, but it seems
OL,14,Flike the most impossible thing for the
OL,15,Ffashion industry to do."
OL,26,@oD@AOU
