PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1782733687
OL,3,CFashion show celebrates disability,
OL,4,Cinclusion and adaptive fashion
OL,6,FOrganisers say every person walking
OL,7,Fthe catwalk has their own unique
OL,8,Fstory, with the event aiming to
OL,9,Fcelebrate individuality while proving
OL,10,Fadaptive fashion can be both practical
OL,11,Fand stylish.
OL,13,F"Fashion is designed for people, so
OL,14,Fpeople should be at the heart of how
OL,15,Fwe design." says Ellie.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@KO]
